These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-8-1::.
There 2 different types of food: onion, orange
There are 2 different nationalities: thai, indonesian
1. the thai is on the right of the indonesian##1
2. the person eating onion is not to the right of the indonesian##8

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2     |
| Food        | onion   | orange   |
| Nationality   | indonesian | thai |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-8-2::.
There 2 different types of food: apricot, raspberry
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: cycling, lacrosse
1. the person who's sport is cycling is not to the left of the person eating raspberry##8
2. the person who's sport is cycling is somewhere to the right of the person eating raspberry##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2    |
| Food   | raspberry | apricot   |
| Sport      | lacrosse | cycling |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-8-3::.
There 2 different types of food: cabbage, peach
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: november, july
1. the person eating cabbage is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in july##8
2. the person eating peach is on the left of the person who's birthday is in july##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |
| Food          | peach | cabbage |
| Birthday   | november   | july     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-8-4::.
