2 different pets are kept: dog, fish
1. the owner of the dog is not to the right of the art-deco house##8
2. the art-deco house is on the right of the owner of the dog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |  2   |
| House   | gothic-revival | art-deco |
| Pet    | dog    | fish |

