.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-8-5::.
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: ice-hockey, soccer
2 different games are played: poker, go
1. the person playing poker is not to the left of the person playing poker##8
2. the person who's sport is soccer is somewhere to the left of the person playing go##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2      |
| Sport       | soccer     | ice-hockey |
| Game   | poker | go |

